law.text:
The court disposition level of the system shall consist of at least the following information as relates to bond and pretrial release:
Whether or not the defendant was released on bail or pretrial release;
If released on bail:
The amount of the bail;
Whether the bail was cash, property, a percentage of cash bail, secured, unsecured, or otherwise;
Whether the conditions of bail were satisfied; and
Whether or not the bail was returned, forfeited, credited to the public advocate or otherwise;
If released on any other form of pretrial release:
Whether or not released on own recognizance;
Whether release was upon conditions, if so what conditions; and
Whether the conditions of release were satisfied.
